<英文法規名稱>Regulations Governing Land Acquisition by Aliens for Investments in Major National Infrastructure Projects, Overall Economic Development, or Agricultural and Animal Husbandry Industries</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>外國人投資國內重大建設整體經濟或農牧經營取得土地辦法</中文法規名稱>
